NAME
	capitalize - convert the first letter of a string to uppercase

SYNOPSIS
	string capitalize(string arg)

DESCRIPTION
	Converts the first character in arg to uppercase.

RETURN VALUE
	A new, converted string is returned.

EXAMPLES
	string name;

	name = capitalize("woohoo");
	name = capitalize(this_player()->query_name());

SEE ALSO
	safun/add_comma, afun/lowercase, safun/pluralize, afun/uppercase
